Percy Jackson Game

Demigod is prophesied to lead a quest to recover the Golden Fleece which was stolen by xx. The golden fleece is a mythical object that can heal any living thing. It was first recovered from the Sea of monsters by Clarisse La Rue, Percy Jackson, Annabeth Chase and Tyson. Said demigod must complete the training challenges before battling monsters before going on the quest. The demigod must venture into xx location and retrieve the fleece within 7 days. Said demigod has a wide arrat of options from all cabins to pick as companions.
